[445.259269, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\u001b[?25l\u001b[H\u001b[3G\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[1m3. The first real fork in the road — where does \u001b[38;5;153m/converse\u001b[39m live?\u001b[22m\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B- \u001b[1m(a) Converse moves onto the fast path too\u001b[22m once a\u001b[54Gtached\u001b[61G—\u001b[63GHTTP\u001b[68Gkeeps\u001b[74Gonly\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bbootstrap/ceremony.\u001b[23GOne\u001b[27Gcontract,\u001b[37Geverything\u001b[48Gsession-scoped,\u001b[64Greplayable\u001b[75Gfrom\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bthe outbox (a dropped client re-attaches and see\u001b[52G the answer it\u001b[67Gmissed\u001b[74G—\u001b[76Gwhich\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bis your neut\u001b[16Gal-space requirement working\u001b[45Gfor chat, not just ingesti\u001b[72Gn).\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B- \u001b[1m(b) Converse/research stay HTTP+SSE\u001b[22m as today; fas\u001b[55G path is ingestion-only.\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1BLess migration now, but chat then does\u001b[42GNOT survive drops the way \u001b[69Gngestion\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bdoes — two delivery seman\u001b[29Gics\u001b[33Gforev\u001b[39Gr.\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B-\u001b[5GMy\u001b[8Grecommendation\u001b[23Gis\u001b[26G\u001b[1m(a)\u001b[30G\u001b[22m—\u001b[32Git's\u001b[37Gthe\u001b[41Gonly\u001b[46Gone\u001b[50Gwhere\u001b[56G\"clyffy\u001b[64Gstays\u001b[70Gfully\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bworking while my connection is trash\" applies to the conversation\u001b[69Gitself,\u001b[77Gand\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1BDevPulse's\u001b[14Gconverse\u001b[23Gpipeline\u001b[32Gjust\u001b[37Gre-points\u001b[47Gat\u001b[50Ga\u001b[52Gstream.\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[1m4. Backpressure/ack visible to the client:\u001b[22m lean on QUIC's own per-stream flow\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bcontrol for byte-level backpressure, and\u001b[44Gmake the\u001b[53Gonly applica\u001b[66Gion-l\u001b[72Gvel\u001b[76Gack\u001b[K\u001b[23;1H\u001b[19;3H\u001b[?25h\u001b[?2026l"]
[445.373155, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\u001b[?25l\u001b[H\u001b[3G-\u001b[5GMy\u001b[8Grecommendation\u001b[23Gis\u001b[26G\u001b[1m(a)\u001b[30G\u001b[22m—\u001b[32Git's\u001b[37Gthe\u001b[41Gonly\u001b[46Gone\u001b[50Gwhere\u001b[56G\"clyffy\u001b[64Gstays\u001b[70Gfully\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bworking while my connection is trash\" applies to the conversation\u001b[69Gitself,\u001b[77Gand\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1BDevPulse's converse pipeline just re-points\u001b[47Gat a\u001b[52Gs\u001b[54Gream.\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[1m4. Backpressure/ack visible to the client:\u001b[22m lean on QUIC'\u001b[60G own per-\u001b[70Gtream\u001b[76Gflow\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bcontrol\u001b[11Gfor byte-lev\u001b[24Gl backpressure, and make\u001b[49Gt\u001b[51Ge only application-level\u001b[76Gack\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bthe \u001b[1mjour\u001b[12Gal-ACK\u001b[22m (frame seq acked ⇔ journale\u001b[47G, per branch 2'\u001b[64Glaw). N\u001b[72G custom\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bcredit windows\u001b[18Gin v1 — that's machin\u001b[40Gry we'd be inventing b\u001b[63Gfore\u001b[68Gthe benchmark\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bgate\u001b[8Gproves we n\u001b[20Ged\u001b[23Git.\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[1m5. Pure-client law, stated as the contract's invariant:\u001b[22m D\u001b[61GvPulse may render,\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bcache-for-retry (its unjournaled tail), and\u001b[47Gre-\u001b[51Gttach. It\u001b[61Gnever\u001b[67Gdecides,\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Btransforms,\u001b[15Gor\u001b[18Gpersists\u001b[27Gbrain-side\u001b[38Gtruth\u001b[44G—\u001b[46Gif\u001b[49Ga\u001b[51Gfeature\u001b[59Gneeds\u001b[65Gbrain\u001b[71Glogic,\u001b[78Git\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bbecomes a work-item type, not client code.\u001b[46G\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\u001b[23;1H\u001b[19;3H\u001b[?25h\u001b[?2026l"]
[445.398335, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\u001b[?25l\u001b[H\u001b[3Gcredit windows in v1 —\u001b[26Gthat's machin\u001b[40Gry we'd be inv\u001b[55Gnting before the benchmark\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bgate proves we need it.\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[1m5. Pure-client law, stated as the contract's invariant:\u001b[59G\u001b[22mDevPulse\u001b[68Gmay\u001b[72Grender,\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bcache-for-retry (its unjournaled tail), and re-attach. It\u001b[61Gnever decid\u001b[73Gs,\u001b[76G\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Btransforms,\u001b[15Gor persists brain-\u001b[34Gide truth\u001b[44G— if\u001b[49Ga feature needs brain logic, it\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bbecomes a work-item type, not client code.\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1BDecision points on the table:\u001b[33G\u001b[1m(3) converse-on-fast-path a/b\u001b[22m,\u001b[64Gand\u001b[68Gwhether\u001b[76Gthe\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[1mstream map\u001b[14G\u001b[22min\u001b[17G(2)\u001b[21Gmatches\u001b[29Gyour\u001b[34Gmental\u001b[41Gmodel\u001b[47G(per-source\u001b[59Gingestion\u001b[69Gstreams\u001b[77Gvs\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bone muxed ingestion stream). Where do you land on 3?\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;174m✽\u001b[3GGust\u001b[38;5;216ming\u001b[38;5;174m… \u001b[38;5;246m(1m 25s · ↓\u001b[39m \u001b[38;5;246m4.0k tokens)\u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;246m  ⎿  Tip: Use /btw to ask a quick side question without interrupting Claude's \r\u001b[5C\u001b[1Bcurrent work\u001b[39m\u001b[23;1H\u001b[19;3H\u001b[?25h\u001b[?2026l"]
