[31852.736901, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\u001b[?25l\u001b[H\u001b[3G\u001b[1mThe architecture answer.\u001b[28G\u001b[22mThe\u001b[32Gevolution\u001b[42Gfrom\u001b[47GHTTP\u001b[52Gdoesn't\u001b[60Gmove\u001b[65Gyour\u001b[70Gprocessing\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B— it only changes how the \u001b[3mbytes travel\u001b[23m. Y\u001b[45Gur high-p\u001b[55Grformanc\u001b[65Gembedded\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bingestion\u001b[13G(embedder →\u001b[25Gqortex-HNSW → connectome recall spine) runs \u001b[1mon \u001b[22m\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[1mclyffy-01, locally, unchanged\u001b[22m. The wire's only\u001b[50Gjob is\u001b[57Gto d\u001b[62Gliver context\u001b[76Gfrom\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bthe devstation faster than clyffy consumes it — and the measur\u001b[66Gd\u001b[68Gfloor already\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bguarantees that: QUIC's \u001b[3mworst\u001b[23m loopback number\u001b[49G(5.0 Gbps\u001b[59G≈ 625 MB/s) is\u001b[74Gord\u001b[78Grs\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bof m\u001b[8Ggnitude \u001b[17Gbove what\u001b[27Gthe embedding/recall pipeline actually eats\u001b[71Gper\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bsecond. On a\u001b[16G1GbE or 2.5GbE\u001b[31Gdevstation link,\u001b[48GQUIC satura\u001b[60Ges the physical\u001b[76Gwire\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Boutright. The only unproven\u001b[31Gc\u001b[33Gll is 10GbE line-rate, which is \u001b[66Gxactly what the\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1BLAN leg +\u001b[13Ggate exists t\u001b[27G prov\u001b[33G (and\u001b[39Gthe embedded-WG fallback covers if it\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bfails).\u001b[11G\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1BAnd\u001b[7Gthe\u001b[11Gpart\u001b[16Gthat\u001b[21Gmatters\u001b[29Gmost\u001b[34Gto\u001b[37Gyou:\u001b[42G\u001b[1mjournal-then-ACK + outbox + Adrift \r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bmeans the wire is never load-bearing for clyffy's health.\u001b[22m Frames journal on\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Barrival; a weak, slow, or dead connection stalls nothing — ing\u001b[67Gti\u001b[70Gn keeps\u001b[K\u001b[23;1H\u001b[19;3H\u001b[?25h\u001b[?2026l"]
