[31855.051787, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\u001b[?25l\u001b[H\u001b[3Gsecond. On a\u001b[16G1GbE or 2.5GbE\u001b[31Gdevstation link,\u001b[48GQUIC satura\u001b[60Ges the physical\u001b[76Gwire\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Boutright. The only unproven\u001b[31Gc\u001b[33Gll is 10GbE line-rate, which is \u001b[66Gxactly what the\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1BLAN leg +\u001b[13Ggate exists t\u001b[27G prov\u001b[33G (and\u001b[39Gthe embedded-WG fallback covers if it\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bfails).\u001b[11G\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1BAnd\u001b[7Gthe\u001b[11Gpart\u001b[16Gthat\u001b[21Gmatters\u001b[29Gmost\u001b[34Gto\u001b[37Gyou:\u001b[42G\u001b[1mjournal-then-ACK + outbox + Adrift \r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bmeans the wire is never load-bearing for clyffy's health.\u001b[22m Frames journal on\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Barrival; a weak, slow, or dead connection stalls nothing — ing\u001b[67Gti\u001b[70Gn keeps\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bp\u001b[5Gocessing, results accumulate\u001b[34Gin the outbox, and the devstation replays from\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bits cursors\u001b[15Gwhen it\u001b[23Gret\u001b[27Grns. That's your \"clyffy s\u001b[54Gays fully operational\"\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Brequirement\u001b[15Genforced by de\u001b[30Gign, not\u001b[39Gby network luck.\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[1mOn loopbacks\u001b[16G\u001b[22m—\u001b[18Gthey\u001b[23Gwere\u001b[28Ga\u001b[30Gharness\u001b[38Gsanity\u001b[45Gleg,\u001b[50Gnot\u001b[54Gthe\u001b[58Gdecision;\u001b[68Gloopback\u001b[77GTCP\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bis memcpy so\u001b[16Gthe ratio there is meani\u001b[41Ggless. But loopback \u001b[63Gn't useless\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Beith\u001b[8Gr: it prov\u001b[19Gs the floo\u001b[30G,\u001b[32Gand if DevPul\u001b[46Ge\u001b[48Gever runs on\u001b[61Gclyffy-01 it\u001b[74Gelf,\u001b[23;1H\u001b[19;3H\u001b[?25h\u001b[?2026l"]
