[31888.475945, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\u001b[?25l\u001b[H\u001b[3G3 stream cou\u001b[16Gts × 5 runs each,\u001b[34Gplus BBR points and ping-\u001b[60Gong latency \u001b[73Gells —\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Broughly\u001b[11G10–20\u001b[17Gminutes).\u001b[27GWhen\u001b[32Git\u001b[35Gcompletes\u001b[45GI'll\u001b[50Gfold\u001b[55Gthe\u001b[59Gfull\u001b[64Gtable\u001b[70Ginto\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;153mJOURNAL.md\u001b[14G\u001b[39mand\u001b[18Gupdate\u001b[25Gthe dive notes/memory\u001b[47Gwith the\u001b[56Gc\u001b[58Gmpleted loopback event.\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1BTo restate the direc\u001b[24G a\u001b[27Gsw\u001b[32Gwhile it runs: \u001b[1myes\u001b[22m — as long as\u001b[64Gcontext travels\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bdevst\u001b[9Gtion → clyffy, all\u001b[28Gyour systems\u001b[41Gwork, because the \u001b[60Gmbedded\u001b[68G\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bhigh-performance parts never left\u001b[37Gclyffy.\u001b[45GThe wire\u001b[54Gfeeds the pipeline;\u001b[74G\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bjournal-the\u001b[15G-ACK me\u001b[23Gns a bad wire can starve the \u001b[53Gipeline of \u001b[3mnew\u001b[23m context at\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bworst, never stal\u001b[21G or degrade it; and the\u001b[45Gmeasured QUIC floor\u001b[65G(≥5 Gbp\u001b[74Gev\u001b[77Gn\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bbefore \u001b[11Guning) is\u001b[21Gfar abov\u001b[31Gwhat the ingestion pipeline consumes. The only\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bce\u001b[7G that genuin\u001b[20Gly awaits the devstation is\u001b[48Gthe\u001b[52Greal-LAN\u001b[61Gleg\u001b[65G—\u001b[67Gthat's\u001b[74Gthe\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bship\u001b[8Ggate\u001b[13Gfor\u001b[17Gthe\u001b[21GQUIC\u001b[26Glane\u001b[31Gspecifically,\u001b[45Gand\u001b[49Geven\u001b[54Gits\u001b[58Gfailure\u001b[66Gmode\u001b[71Gis\u001b[74Ga\r\u001b[1B \u001b[3Gfallback (embedded WG), not a broken system.\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;246m✻\u001b[3GBrewed for\u001b[14G1m 17s · 1 shell still running\r\u001b[4B\u001b[39m❯ \u001b[23;1H\u001b[19;3H\u0