[33275.505676, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\u001b[?25l\u001b[H\u001b[3G\u001b[3mtier\u001b[23m, not one blessed devstation↔clyffy-01\u001b[46Gpair.\u001b[52GThe\u001b[56Gloopback\u001b[65Gtier\u001b[70Gis\u001b[73Gcomplete\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B(33 cells in \u001b[38;5;153mJOURNAL.md\u001b[39m); wire tiers get measured as real second machines\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bcome online — no topology hardcoded\u001b[39Ginto\u001b[44Gthe\u001b[48Gcriterion.\r\u001b[5C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1BThat closes branch 3's work honestly: contract + skeletons + harness built\u001b[78Gand\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bverified, loopback event complete, the correction folded in, and the open\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bitems (per-tier wire legs, gate recalibration, \u001b[38;5;153msignal fold\u001b[39m SIGABRT defect,\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bsession engine) all named in the notes for the fold.\u001b[K\r\u001b[5C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1BExit this session when ready — that triggers branch 4 (deployment-shape),\u001b[77Gthe\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Blast branch before the terminal fold.\u001b[K\r\u001b[43C\u001b[2B\u001b[38;5;246mthought for 11s)\u001b[39m\u001b[23;1H\u001b[19;3H\u001b[?25h\u001b[?2026l"]
