[33318.628491, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\u001b[?25l\u001b[H\u001b[3G\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bverified,\u001b[13Gloopback\u001b[22Gevent\u001b[28Gcomplete,\u001b[38Gthe\u001b[42Gcorrection\u001b[53Gfolded\u001b[60Gin,\u001b[64Gand\u001b[68Gthe\u001b[72Gopen\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bitems (per-tier wire legs, gate recalibra\u001b[45Gion,\u001b[50G\u001b[38;5;153msignal fold\u001b[62G\u001b[39mSIGABRT defect,\u001b[78G\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bs\u001b[5Gssion engine) all named in the no\u001b[39Ges\u001b[42Gf\u001b[45G the fold.\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1BExit this session when ready\u001b[32G— that triggers branch 4\u001b[57G(deployment-shape),\u001b[77Gthe\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Blast\u001b[8Gbranch\u001b[15Gbefore\u001b[22Gthe\u001b[26Gterminal\u001b[35Gfold.\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;246m✻\u001b[3GChurned for 1m 7s\u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[2B\u001b[48;5;237m\u001b[38;5;239m❯ \u001b[38;5;231mdid you even do the code since you coded earlier and get it finished?\u001b[39m         \r\u001b[2B\u001b[49m\u001b[38;5;231m●\u001b[39m Fair challenge — let me audit honestly rather than assert. The Rust code\u001b[K\u001b[23;1H\u001b[19;3H\u001b[?25h\u001b[?2026l"]
