[33351.998282, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\u001b[?25l\u001b[H\r\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;231m●\u001b[3G\u001b[39mFair challenge — let me \u001b[28Gudit hones\u001b[39Gly rather than assert. The Rust code\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bitself is finished\u001b[22Ga\u001b[25G was already topology-agnostic (generic \u001b[38;5;153mhost:port\u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Beverywhere, enroll endpoint in\u001b[34Gplace, no LAN assumptions). But two th\u001b[73Gngs are\u001b[K\r\u001b[3C\u001b[1Benuinely unfinished: the repo doc a\u001b[40Gdendum s\u001b[49Gill c\u001b[55Grries the devstation-bound\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bgate wording your correction \u001b[33Gup\u001b[36Grseded, \u001b[45Gnd the plan's verification step 5\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B(\u001b[38;5;153m/converse\u001b[14G\u001b[39mSSE\u001b[18Gregression)\u001b[30Gwas\u001b[34Gnever\u001b[40Gactually\u001b[49Gexercised.\u001b[60GFinishing\u001b[70Gboth\u001b[75Gnow.\r\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B  \u001b[38;5;246mSearched for \u001b[1m1\u001b[22m pattern, read \u001b[1m1\u001b[22m file, ran \u001b[1m1\u001b[22m shell command \r\u001b[2B \r\u001b[4C\u001b[2B\u001b[38;5;174metc\u001b[39m\u001b[23;1H\u001b[19;3H\u001b[?25h\u001b[?2026l"]
[33352.041882, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\u001b[?25l\u001b[H\u001b[6G\u001b[38;5;77m\u001b[48;5;22m     +\u001b[38;5;231mp99.** Miss on a tier → that tier                             \r\u001b[1B\u001b[49m\u001b[39m \u001b[3G   \u001b[38;5;77m\u001b[48;5;22m 237 +\u001b[38;5;231m>    falls back (embedded WG/NepTUN) — a per-tier decision, no\u001b[49m\u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B   \u001b[38;5;77m\u001b[48;5;22m     +\u001b[38;5;231mt a global no-ship. Links at/below                            \r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[49m\u001b[39m   \u001b[38;5;77m\u001b[48;5;22m 238 +\u001b[38;5;231m>    5GbE are pre-cleared by the measured loopback floor; ≥10G\u001b[49m\u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B   \u001b[38;5;77m\u001b[48;5;22m     +\u001b[38;5;231mbE tiers require the wire run.                                \u001b[49m\u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B   \u001b[38;5;77m\u001b[48;5;22m 239 +\u001b[38;5;231m                                                              \u001b[49m\u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B   \u001b[38;5;231m\u001b[2m 240 \u001b[22m ## A6. Config (SSOT)\u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[5C\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;231m\u001b[2m 241 \u001b[22m `[session]` → `granularity = \"workspace\" | \"task\"` (per-user o\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[39m   \u001b[38;5;231m\u001b[2m     \u001b[22m ption), `max_live_attachments = 1`.\u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[5C\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;231m\u001b[2m 242 \u001b[22m `[fastpath]` → `enabled = false` until the bench gate passes. \r\u001b[1B\u001b[39m \u001b[3G   \u001b[38;5;231m\u001b[2m     \u001b[22m `[api]` bind/port now HONORED by the\u001b[39m\u001b[K\u001b[23;1H\u001b[19;3H\u001b[?25h\u001b[?2026l"]
